  "title": "Account Manager (Telephony/ PABX System) #80152",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: IT Communications Service Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Account Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central (Nearest MRT: Mattar)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days / Monday to Friday, 9am – 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Transport Allowance + Monthly Commission + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and execute successful strategies to manage and grow existing accounts.</li><li>Identify, define, and deliver business requirements aligned with customer needs.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with customers at all organizational levels.</li><li>Engage key decision-makers and present tailored value propositions that address their business challenges.</li><li>Nurture long-term partnerships through trust, collaboration, and consistent value delivery.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min ITE in Engineering.</li><li>Min 1 year of experience in a related field or sales account management role.</li><li>Prior experience in dealing with telephony system and communication solution will be a plus.</li><li>Alcatel, Mitel and Yeastar PABX knowledge will be an added advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80152 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
